Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好痛...!
Comment: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:05.74,up,,0,0,0,,##聯合國秘書長布萊恩‧傑克森指出 有一位少年|The UN Chairman Brain Jackson reported that a young...##
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:05.74,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,聯合國秘書長布萊恩‧傑克森指出 有一位少年
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:05.74,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fs28\pos(960,12)}The UN Chairman Brain Jackson reported that a young...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,痛死了...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.74,0:05:08.37,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,毫髮無傷地將該組織的首領及身旁的幹部全員逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:12.49,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,他表示 今後將全力預防敵方殘存戰力所引發的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.95,0:05:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還有這麼方便的能力喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.70,0:05:15.16,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,也期望能以和平的手段解決問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好像還有其他地方有能力者聚集的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「獨眼的死神」啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這稱號也太令人羞恥了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.37,0:05:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒想到我竟然會被人叫成這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,剛剛的影像是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在不知不覺中 我也變得能知道自己奪取了什麼能力了嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我又將一個國家中的所有能力全部奪走了哦 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,得到了能翻譯語言的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也得到了不用睡覺的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.40,0:06:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但你也別太逞強了哦 有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不 下一個國家也得加緊腳步才行 時間不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說得也是 雖然會很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但 在你的能力消失之前 就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓病情惡化的能力嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又是一群聚在一起的能力者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,竟然讓孩子們做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,另一邊只有一個亮點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.62,0:07:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼回事? 完全沒有畫面浮上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.25,0:07:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這設施到底是做什麼的?
Comment: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,##感染者?|Carrier?##
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,感染者?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fs32\pos(944,962)}Carrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,原來是這麼一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,原來如此 雖然已經感染了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但能力還沒發病 所以叫感染者嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fs32\pos(1258,962)}Carrier?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但我沒辦法奪取還沒發病的能力 該怎麼辦才好...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒錯 就是因為特殊能力是一種疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以才要趕在粒子再次散佈到全球之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓全世界的人都接種這疫苗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對吼 如果能力是疾病 那只要加重它的病情 使它發病
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不就可以奪取了嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好 進行得很順利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了不讓能力者在我離開的國家中再次出現
Comment: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,之後得連##感染者|carrier##的能力都一起奪走才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,之後得連感染者的能力都一起奪走才行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\fs32\pos(768,962)}carrier
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我全力射擊到子彈用完為止!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是謝謝妳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,治癒能力果然存在啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.52,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,您能痊癒真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉了 雖然妳是用能力在做好事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但我也不得不將其奪走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.23,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,...非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這隻手...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果現在將這隻手放在右眼上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我便連時空跳躍的能力都能取回
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣說不定就能救熊耳先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我並不是為了這種事情才去奪取能力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.06,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:42.39,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不能再做出違反人之常情的行為了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將世界變成一個沒有能力者的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.57,0:09:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這才是我唯一的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吵死了 吵死了 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.29,0:10:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吵死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,吵死了啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 你沒事吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是敵人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是...我的敵人嗎!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.99,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,請饒命啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對 冷靜 冷靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.33,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不能殺害任何人
Comment: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,<CM>
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,...宣布已經抓住了首都的哈桑‧馬斯爾市長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:01.59,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,根據政府線人的密報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.93,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明天要到這裡嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.97,0:11:05.85,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,昨天 武裝政變集團攻擊了市長官邸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,偶爾...就算勉強也行...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:08.64,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,市長被當場抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.47,0:11:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,稍微...睡一下吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:10.73,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,根據政府的說法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.98,0:11:14.61,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,這次攻擊至少造成了10名市政委員死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,偶爾也必須...讓身體休息一下...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.86,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,重傷人數更高達20多人 現在...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:24.66,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,...於今早 政變的主謀莫夫森‧賓‧亞基特表示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:27.41,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,願意無條件投降
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:30.46,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,這場從去年持續至今的首都戰事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.79,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,是由一個以孩童為中心組成的組織所引發的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:37.50,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,但就在昨天 因某不明人士所引發的一場戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.72,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,對組織造成了極大的損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是我...做的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.18,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,對此 該政變組織...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:48.81,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,...莫夫森將不會因為其他罪行受到起訴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不妙 記憶很混亂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.93,0:11:52.02,up,,0,0,0,karaoke,政府會如何處理 將是今後外界所關注的焦點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,果然不能睡覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...在這裡做什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼我會在戰場上呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.80,0:12:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對了 我和她約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.01,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要奪走世界上所有的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.47,0:12:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,再回到她的身邊...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.98,0:12:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她...是誰來著?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.65,0:12:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明應該是很重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.07,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,卻想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,爆炸能力者會在那裡出現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣啊 你就是那個「死神」嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.35,0:13:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼 就和我們的信仰一起去死...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那種力量只會給人帶來不幸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,獨眼...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你該不會是...「死神」!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.30,0:13:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對 我就是「死神」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,哈囉 「死神」來囉~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.04,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好累啊 我不想幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這種累死人的鳥事到底是誰想出來的?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又為什麼得由我來做啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.18,0:14:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我已經累了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,誰來跟我換手一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我想到一個好主意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,乾脆把整個地球都奪走好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我這麼全能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就是神 萬事皆由我說了算!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就這麼做吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這什麼東西?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,髒死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.89,0:15:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼...我會後悔把這東西給踢飛了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼...我會為此掉眼淚啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是怎樣啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是要我再繼續加把勁嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,死...「死神」啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,給我!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.33,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼打不中啊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙是怪物嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那傢伙是「獨眼的死神」 我們是打不過他的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,讓開!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.93,0:16:42.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這下總該打倒他了吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,騙人的吧...這可是RPG啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.61,0:16:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.45,0:16:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,十分感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.01,0:17:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這附近嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好耶!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.41,0:17:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,終於幹掉那個「死神」了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.88,0:17:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不准欺負弱者!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼欺負弱者...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳知道這傢伙是什麼人嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不知道 但你不可以做這種事!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這傢伙的腦袋超值錢的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要幹掉他 我就能大賺一筆了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,即使如此也不可以!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.65,0:18:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那 只好讓妳也吃點苦頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.82,0:18:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,隨你高興 但我是絕對不會讓開的!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.70,0:18:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼回事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒想到...最後一位能力者的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,竟然是「勇氣」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但妳這叫做有用無謀 差點就丟掉小命了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不可以...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.89,0:18:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳已經是個充滿勇氣的女孩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以 快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我去找人來幫忙 我一定會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,結束了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.29,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是約定 我該回去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經結束了 該回去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,全部搞定了 該回去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,回去...是要回哪裡?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,該回去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.61,0:19:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該...已經...約好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣我就一輩子不愁吃穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎...怎麼回事!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.33,0:19:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有宇!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你終於醒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.29,0:20:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.95,0:20:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你遵守約定了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你的生命並沒有大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.05,0:20:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但請暫時靜養一陣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,話說回來 妳是哪位?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:20:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.94,0:21:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,說得也是 畢竟你奪取了成千上萬的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對腦的負擔應該不小吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還能正常說話就該偷笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.66,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是你的女朋友!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.21,0:21:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,女朋友? 但我對妳完全沒有印象欸?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這話比想像中的還要傷人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我剛才...讓妳傷心了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.22,0:21:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.93,0:21:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為 你可是和我同班
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,和我一起在學生會度過高中生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,並在承諾和我交往後 就一走了之的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對不起 我什麼都想不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這單字本就是我做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.20,0:21:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你一直到最後一刻都帶著它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,它有幫上你的忙嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.33,0:21:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.41,0:21:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是妳...給我的?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這對我來說 就像護身符一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.96,0:22:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只有這個 我一直都捨不得丟掉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明明都這麼破破爛爛的了...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,謝謝你...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果你是靠它...才能像現在這樣回到這裡的話...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那正是我所祈望的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我又...讓妳傷心了?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.15,0:22:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不 我只是很高興而已 就只是這樣而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然搞不太懂 但 別哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.16,0:22:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,乙坂有宇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.96,0:22:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,歡迎回來!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:23:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然這攝影機拍下的盡是些我不想拍的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.52,0:23:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但從今以後 我會將鏡頭放在大家身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以拍下許多幸福的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以 讓我們一起留下許多美好的回憶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.91,0:23:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.16,0:23:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可以算步步一份嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.37,0:23:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,當然囉
